{"tid":1746733,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"聽日 投票重點briefing","createTime":"2019-11-23T01:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:45:11.000Z","uid":162645,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1da6f063de1f9bb91151c8e20236006447479814","tid":1746733,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">重點：做港豬，心平氣和</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWJYhjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWJYhjQ.png&h=7cc0ebe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除左上面張圖，<br />\n大家記得一定要 心平氣和，<br />\n港共政權最想 delay開票/腰斬選舉<br />\n總之我地就要保住個選舉 順利進行<br />\n（我地追求民主，所以要尊重 公平選舉）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要0730 投票！</span></span><br />\n之前d人話 咁早阻住 要返工既人 投<br />\n如果真係有手足要返工，<br />\n我諗出句聲 一定有人讓<br />\n<br />\n但係如果 俾人腰斬，真係後悔都揼春<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">估算：</span><br />\n聽日 老人院 投完票，<br />\n可能會有小量鄉黑攪事，<br />\n跟住防暴 話情況混亂 唔俾人入去投票<br />\n相信呢個時候大家會好嬲，<br />\n想打鳩個黑警<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但請緊記</span><br />\n聽日做港豬，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可圍觀，可拍攝，可細聲抱怨</span><br />\n總之，不為 腰斬選舉負責<br />\n<br />\n如果港共政權 風頭火勢都腰斬<br />\n將會係另一國際核彈，我地要送佢一程！"},{"pid":"2037b617aad00f1633eb2578377a234d2934174c","tid":1746733,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"自推1/5"},{"pid":"881ec7571618eb8d24ec9d49adcf889b9a9bde8b","tid":1746733,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d5d1acd6a05a0cec922b160815d26f254e7c8f","tid":1746733,"uid":323373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:32:19.000Z","msg":"防暴守站，用意挑釁，隨時截查，稍有差池，連人帶走，冇得投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記緊要冷處理，要鬆容，不中計，聽日我要投到票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70eec1a7daead6be6a82648a54dd29228b83348","tid":1746733,"uid":65889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:37:27.000Z","msg":"今次「同統計員講投建制」有少少問題，因為多區都得兩個候選人，唔似選立法會有得配票。如果咁做，令建制覺得夠票而提早玩嘢關站，會令好多真正想投既人冇得投。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>所以係咪得兩個候選人既票站講投咗民主，三個以上既講投咗民建聯？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申：投建制/白票不得好死"},{"pid":"e76cdbe3c633a948a350e6be44c05fc6c7d0031f","tid":1746733,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:40:16.000Z","msg":"再推2/5"},{"pid":"4e7afecba1de48361449d552d9abd5a4a5632e94","tid":1746733,"uid":113016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52ff255758b87ab91cf1b320d692b64fbc0f0a0a","tid":1746733,"uid":162645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:43:22.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"ef8cf621947d204837c6dbc536776204170d1e67","tid":1746733,"uid":296181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"心平氣和，忍一日咁多，以後慢慢再同狗玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}